          "reviewBody": "I studied in this school for more than 10 years. Regular extra-curricular activities are conducted here. Teachers are experienced & competent to teach students very well. The non- teaching  staff too, is polite, helpful, & caring. I have many friends who are having the right attitude after passing out from here. They are doing well in their careers. You can easily see the difference between students of D.Y.Patil and others. I am really grateful that I was a part of this school. I have made memories here which will definitely last a lifetime.",
